When you start the game, you will automatically log in into a new game session.
During the game, players take turns performing actions on the map.
At the beginning of your turn, you may move to adjacent space, revealing its contents.
Afterwards, you may perform one of the following actions:
-Buy ice cream if there is a store at your current tile.
-Sell ice cream to a customer if there are no zombies around.
-Kill a zombie.
-Run back to your previous space.
Selling ice cream and killing zombies contribute to your score.
The game ends after a certain number of turns. The player with the highest score wins.
